lockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔撚啱聽就屌人老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係威就唔洗呀爸揀車啦<br />\n車都未揸穩揸熟就話要改呢樣改嗰樣 <br />\n邊頭揸車？唔去嗰邊費事撞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1b7bc2f7de99aa01880c9f1c0939f7ea9ddbea","tid":98971,"uid":66750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\nXX5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> XX3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nXX3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係咩？XPX 喎"},{"pid":"7451258e95788a1095ac184399b2f8be59a5512a","tid":98971,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心唔好哂錢改<br />\n<br />\n全原裝已經代步一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  拎黎開工放工無得輸 渣緊01年<br />\n<br />\n無就住踩  開住冷氣70%高速 30%市區 坐1-3人 都係510蚊 行到545公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又無野整 換下電池 偈油 油隔 風隔 火咀 呔 波箱油 d消耗品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1500cc車算係咁啦  不過真係飛唔起囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儲緊錢換edix 2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換哂消耗品幾錢到？<br />\n揸緊02 mt vti</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就換左4條呔  2條15吋ps3(頭呔)$1200  2條15吋大陸sunny(尾呔)$500    <br />\n<br />\n波箱油$400  5w40偈油 連油隔 denso火嘴 $820 風隔$100<br />\n藍電$800</blockquote><br />\n原來ps 系列用到落 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上官網search 得energy xm2啱size <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f07e721ec2ef13d3b8ec21a7268e82cc0d79e04","tid":98971,"uid":66750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\nXX5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> XX3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n各位巴打都經歷過新牌階段比個忠告唔想你屋企清明重陽去多到姐。你屋企人揀車比你買都係同樣道理。翻噴不了，一定自己hi花撞花。換喉換coilover不了，細cc NA車換喉真係得把聲。呢架車都係攞黎操車，你渣1-2年就會換。想洗d錢落去咪換個大牌子入門USB有藍牙既機頭、喇叭，呢d你換車既時候可以用返。留意返4條呔、碟皮、計油、波箱油（原廠Honda油）、brake油、水箱水（原廠Honda）、火咀、攝嘩佬。"},{"pid":"528f3547b5ec47c2fb83f4a87b0b33c1efe4fb73","tid":98971,"uid":37631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3j332a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3j332a7.jpg&h=cc8c3da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我換開呢隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度有得買 師兄</blockquote><br />\n我都係人地幫我買 我唔知邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可否介紹車房<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b803dea1e3460bc224bda12332c44291b6270ce3","tid":98971,"uid":62370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/211118_90afd3422def02cc03c87ab58ca6db72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F211118_90afd3422def02cc03c87ab58ca6db72.jpg&h=438fc6f0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}